---
title: Sticky Sweet Chilli Chicken Thighs with Roast Pumpkin Wedges & Garlic Veggies
description: Get ready for a plate full of deliciousness! This sticky-sweet delight uses sesame seeds, soy sauce, honey and sweet chilli sauce to top a flavourful mix of tender chicken thighs and garlic-infused veggies for a hearty and crave-worthy dinner.

*Unfortunately, this week's Asian greens were in short supply, so we've replaced them with broccoli. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sticky-sweet-chilli-chicken-thighs-4b648a4d.jpg
